Second Department,

May, 1969

(May 28, 1969 ) The People of the State of New York ex rel. David Antonio, Relator, v. Warden of Brooklyn House of Detention for Men, Respondent.

Application for a writ of habeas corpus denied. Brennan, Acting P. J., Hopkins, Benjamin, Munder and Kleinfeld, JJ., concur.
